flowchart TD
    A[Showroom raises Work Order] --> B[Submit WO]
    B --> C{Auto/Manual Assign Partner}
    C -->|Auto Assignment| D[Find highest priority partner]
    C -->|Manual Assignment| E[Showroom selects partner]
    D --> F[Create Job Card - AWAITING_ACK]
    E --> F
    F --> G[Partner Acknowledges]
    G --> H[Schedule Visit Date/Time]
    H --> I[Start Work - IN_PROGRESS]
    I --> J[Complete Work & Upload Proofs]
    J --> K[Request Approval - PENDING_APPROVAL]
    K --> L{Showroom Review}
    L -->|Approve| M[Freeze pricing & commission snapshots]
    M --> N[Compute payouts]
    N --> O[APPROVED status]
    O --> P[Generate commission records]
    P --> Q[CLOSED]
    L -->|Reject| R[REJECTED - Work Order closed]
    L -->|Request Rework| S[REWORK_REQUESTED]
    S --> T[Back to IN_PROGRESS]
    T --> J

    %% Partner Allocation Flow
    AA[Partner Allocation] --> BB{Level}
    BB -->|Showroom Level| CC[Assign to specific showroom]
    BB -->|Dealership Level| DD[Assign to all showrooms in dealership]
    CC --> EE[Set priority order]
    DD --> EE
    EE --> FF[Partner allocation active]

    %% Pricing Resolution Flow
    GG[Price Resolution] --> HH{Exact Match Rule?}
    HH -->|Yes| II[Partner + Showroom + Vehicle + Service]
    HH -->|No| JJ{Showroom + Service?}
    JJ -->|Yes| KK[Partner + Showroom + Service]
    JJ -->|No| LL{Dealership + Vehicle + Service?}
    LL -->|Yes| MM[Partner + Dealership + Vehicle + Service]
    LL -->|No| NN{Dealership + Service?}
    NN -->|Yes| OO[Partner + Dealership + Service]
    NN -->|No| PP[ERROR: No pricing rule found]

    %% Commission Resolution Flow
    QQ[Commission Resolution] --> RR{Exact Match?}
    RR -->|Yes| SS[Showroom + Sales Person + Service]
    RR -->|No| TT{Sales Person Default?}
    TT -->|Yes| UU[Showroom + Sales Person]
    TT -->|No| VV{Service Default?}
    VV -->|Yes| WW[Showroom + Service]
    VV -->|No| XX{Showroom Default?}
    XX -->|Yes| YY[Showroom Default Rate]
    XX -->|No| ZZ[Zero Commission]

    %% SLA Monitoring
    AAA[SLA Monitor] --> BBB{AWAITING_ACK > X hours?}
    BBB -->|Yes| CCC[Alert Showroom + Partner]
    BBB -->|No| DDD{SCHEDULED but not started?}
    DDD -->|Yes| EEE[Alert about missed schedule]
    DDD -->|No| FFF[Continue monitoring]

    %% Audit Trail
    GGG[User Action] --> HHH[Create Audit Log]
    HHH --> III[Store: Actor, Entity, Action, Diff]
    III --> JJJ[Audit Trail Complete]

    %% Multi-tenant Security
    KKK[API Request] --> LLL{Valid JWT?}
    LLL -->|No| MMM[401 Unauthorized]
    LLL -->|Yes| NNN{OEM Access Check}
    NNN -->|Fail| OOO[403 Forbidden]
    NNN -->|Pass| PPP{Role Permission Check}
    PPP -->|Fail| OOO
    PPP -->|Pass| QQQ[Process Request]

    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style Q fill:#c8e6c9
    style R fill:#ffcdd2
    style PP fill:#ffcdd2
    style ZZ fill:#fff3e0
    style MMM fill:#ffcdd2
    style OOO fill:#ffcdd2
